Question 7:Write program using the NLTK library to perform part-of-speech tagging on a text.


Code :
import nltk
nltk.download('punkt')
nltk.download('averaged_perceptron_tagger')

text = "NLP makes computers understand human language"
tokens = nltk.word_tokenize(text)

tags = nltk.pos_tag(tokens)
print(tags)



Output : 
[('NLP', 'NNP'), ('makes', 'VBZ'), ('computers', 'NNS'),
 ('understand', 'VB'), ('human', 'JJ'), ('language', 'NN')]
